ASSOCIATION OF NEW JERSEY CHIROPRACTORS, INC., and Steven Clarke, DC, Appellants-Petitioners,
v.
STATE HEALTH BENEFITS COMMISSION, State Health Commission, State Health Benefits Program Plan Design Committee, School Employee Health Benefits Commission, School Employee Health Benefits Program Design Committee, and State of New Jersey, Division of Pensions & Benefits, Respondents-Respondents. C-135 September Term 2018
081240 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 05, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005653-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
